output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes, contains "CMF 11240017" at the end of the post 2. Refers to candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions "Marcel Ciolacu" and refers to "alegerile prezidențiale" 3. Addresses wide population: Yes, it's a paid advertisement with significant reach (15,000-19,999 impressions) 4. Electoral objective: Yes, clearly promotes PSD and Marcel Ciolacu for presidential elections, with the slogan "PSD, Calea Sigură pentru România!" 5. Journalism: No, this is clearly campaign material, not journalistic content 6. Personal opinion: No, this is an organized campaign post with CMF number
The post describes campaign activities in Vadu Crișului and explicitly promotes both the presidential and parliamentary campaigns. Given that the presidential campaign period has ended, this constitutes a violation of Article 55 t).
Key factors: - Contains CMF number indicating official campaign material - Explicitly promotes presidential candidate Marcel Ciolacu - Is being actively promoted after the presidential campaign period - Significant reach through paid promotion - Clear electoral intent with campaign slogan

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: 1. Official campaign material (has CMF) 2. Direct reference to presidential elections 3. Paid promotion with wide reach 4. Clear campaign messaging and slogans 5. Direct promotion of presidential candidate
conclusion.message-for-police: Infomed Pro SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui material de propagandă electorală (ID postare Facebook: 1938529673225729) după încheierea perioadei de campanie prezidențială. Materialul, publicat și promovat după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, conține referiri directe la candidatul prezidențial Marcel Ciolacu și alegerile prezidențiale, folosește număr CMF (11240017), și are un obiectiv electoral clar exprimat prin sloganul "PSD, Calea Sigură pentru România!". Postarea a fost promovată activ, atingând între 15.000 și 19.999 de persoane, reprezentând astfel o continuare deliberată a propagandei electorale după încheierea perioadei legale de campanie.
